#### What's an app?
An application is a set of nodes connected together and interact with OpenAI or other alternative. <br><br>Nodes are in the core of an applicatin. Nodes are like black boxes that execute actions. Nodes can connect to a data base,<br>
do a cvs file, or can connect other nodes togheter and create an app.<br><br>Some services that nodes interact with will ask for a API key sometimes. So you need to import those API keys into GaiaHub's credentials.]]></description><link>https://docs.gaiahub.ai/guides/anatomy-of-an-application.html</link><guid isPermaLink="false">Guides/Anatomy of an application.md</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Gaia Team]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:50:08 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title><![CDATA[Concepts]]></title><description><![CDATA[ 
